{"tid":1342650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好俾元朗件事蓋過上環","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:58:55.000Z","uid":107178,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"282f93381c40c0dfb7a879b39421b0918bfda7ee","tid":1342650,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"元朗件事100%要清算<br />\n但請同時關注上環發生嘅事<br />\n<br />\n班狗講完唔會放催淚彈，轉頭發曬癲咁放同<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開左槍</span></span><br />\n睇live鄺仔勸各位散<br />\n有上環手足好激動話要去元朗支援<br />\n個下真係好撚感動想喊咁滯<br />\n因為頭先先食完催淚彈<br />\n仲要個樣望落好後生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推元朗post個陣<br />\n唔該一齊推埋上環post<br />\n唔好俾港共用元朗蓋過中聯辦嘅事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eM7L9xq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeM7L9xq.png&h=d978a1c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab6da76a9d62a1e2865a44266756641178263173","tid":1342650,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d86eaddee7be8d262e16ce25b3f065e05be0e4","tid":1342650,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"80cf46062021b3250cf7fa8039215421beafc96b","tid":1342650,"uid":43657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:51:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8c1f8a303bce861c2f962b95c2d2012377238105","tid":1342650,"uid":73333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:51:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2720bb64170ff1014a361ac1b00d273332dfb4e0","tid":1342650,"uid":263200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:51:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19980f734f5b1ce56242fd6f5ba008cecf3cfe86","tid":1342650,"uid":167475,"like":0,"dislik